"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-04-10-new-tickets-released-100-days-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP)- The chief organiser of the Paris Olympics announced the release of new tickets on Wednesday, while reassuring that everything was on track for \\\"spectacular\\\" Games in just over 100 days.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7036964355469882, \"rank\": 0.33161226356699386, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"The chief organiser\", \"from\": 21, \"to\": 40}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 44, \"to\": 62}, {\"ngram\": \"the release\", \"from\": 73, \"to\": 84}, {\"ngram\": \"new tickets\", \"from\": 88, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 112}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 136, \"to\": 146}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 154, \"to\": 159}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"spectacular\\\" Games\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 183}, {\"ngram\": \"just over 100 days\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Next week, on April 17 at 10 am, we will put 250,000 new tickets on sale for all sports, all price categories and for all competition sites,\\\" Tony Estanguet told reporters, urging interested fans to be \\\"quick\\\" because of high demand.\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 351, \"end\": 365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 223, \"to\": 228}, {\"ngram\": \"10 am\", \"from\": 235, \"to\": 240}, {\"ngram\": \"250,000 new tickets\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 273}, {\"ngram\": \"sale\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 281}, {\"ngram\": \"all sports\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 296}, {\"ngram\": \"all price categories\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 318}, {\"ngram\": \"all competition sites\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 348}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"interested fans\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"high demand\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the clock ticking down to the opening ceremony on July 26, Estanguet said he was confident that the huge organisational and security challenges faced by the organising committee would be overcome.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the clock\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 495}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 503}, {\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"the huge organisational and security challenges\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"the organising committee\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are ready.\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are ready for this final straight,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this final straight\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have built up a lot of confidence and peace of mind.\\\"\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He noted that construction work was often \\\"the biggest challenge that poses problems for the organisation of the Games\\\", but that the Paris 2024 team had taken possession of its facilities on deadline and in some cases ahead of time.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 904, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6010374512844567e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"construction work\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest challenge\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 834}, {\"ngram\": \"problems\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisation\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"possession\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"its facilities\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"deadline\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"some cases\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 988}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The timetable has been perfectly respected which is a relief for us,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The timetable\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"a relief\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also expressed \\\"confidence\\\" in French security forces who will be responsible for the safety of fans and athletes at a time when France is on its highest warning level for terror attacks.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1218, \"end\": 1224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7036964355469882, \"rank\": 0.33161226356699386, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedi