eek is expected to be one of the last major opportunities to secure seats.\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ticket release\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1629}, {\"ngram\": \"the last major opportunities\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1693}, {\"ngram\": \"seats\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following criticism of high prices during previous rounds, Estanguet stressed that half of them would be sold for under 100 euros ($108).\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"criticism\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"high prices\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"previous rounds\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"under 100 euros\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A total of 10,000 tickets for gymnastics will be made available, with 15,000 for swimming, 12,000 for tennis and 35,000 for beach volley, which is set to be played in a temporary stadium in front of the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A total\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1858}, {\"ngram\": \"10,000 tickets\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"beach volley\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1987}, {\"ngram\": \"a temporary stadium\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two-thirds of previous buyers were French, but people from 150 different countries have also secured tickets, according to the organising committee.\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Two-thirds\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2079}, {\"ngram\": \"previous buyers\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2122}, {\"ngram\": \"150 different countries\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"the organising committee\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics are set to take place from July 26-August 11 followed by the Paralympics from August 28-September 8.\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2263}, {\"ngram\": \"-August\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2304}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES Comments are closed.\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES Comments\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2354}]}]}"